files/Mouthwash_tablets_in_use_540x.jpg?v=1767239151\"\r\n               alt=\"Mouthwash tablets in amber glass jar perfect for travel\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;display:block;\">\r\n          <div style=\"padding:16px;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 6px;\">Perfect for travel</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"color:#5a6b63;margin:0;\">Lightweight amber glass jar fits easily in your bag—TSA-friendly and leak-proof.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </article>\r\n\r\n        <article style=\"flex:1 1 300px;min-width:240px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7c9b8;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;\">\r\n          <img src=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/4B5A5239_540x.jpg?v=1767239151\"\r\n               alt=\"Mouthwash tablets for daily oral care routine\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;display:block;\">\r\n          <div style=\"padding:16px;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 6px;\">Daily oral care</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"color:#5a6b63;margin:0;\">Alcohol-free formula supports fresh breath without harsh chemicals.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </article>\r\n\r\n        <article style=\"flex:1 1 300px;min-width:240px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7c9b8;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;\">\r\n          <img src=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/zero_waste_mouthwash_tablets_1512x.jpg?v=1767239151\"\r\n               alt=\"Reusable amber glass jar with mouthwash tablets\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;display:block;\">\r\n          <div style=\"padding:16px;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 6px;\">Reusable glass jar</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"color:#5a6b63;margin:0;\">65 tablets in a recyclable amber glass jar—beautiful and sustainable storage.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </article>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div style=\"margin-top:16px;display:flex;justify-content:center;\">\r\n        <a href=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/products/zero-waste-mouthwash-tablets\"\r\n          rel=\"noopener\"\r\n          style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:999px;\r\n                 background:linear-gradient(180deg,#A1AB97,#1e6e4b);color:#fff;font-weight:800;border:0;\r\n                 box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(22,35,28,.10);text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;\">\r\n          Shop Mouthwash Tablets\r\n        </a>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- FEATURES -->\r\n  <div style=\"padding:22px 0;\" id=\"mme-sec-4\" class=\"mme-scroll-target\">\r\n    <div style=\"max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 16px;\">\r\n      <p style=\"text-align:center;font-weight:800;color:#A1AB97;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0;\">Features &amp; benefits</p>\r\n      <h2 style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:6px;\">Simple and built for modern oral care</h2>\r\n\r\n      <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px;margin-top:14px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"flex:1 1 280px;min-width:240px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7c9b8;border-radius:14px;padding:18px;\">\r\n          <h3 style=\"margin-top:0;\">Alcohol-free formula</h3>\r\n          <p style=\"color:#5a6b63;margin:0;\">No burning sensation—gentle on your mouth with plant derived ingredients.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"flex:1 1 280px;min-width:240px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7c9b8;border-radius:14px;padding:18px;\">\r\n          <h3 style=\"margin-top:0;\">Plant-powered ingredients</h3>\r\n          <p style=\"color:#5a6b63;margin:0;\">Peppermint oil powder, xylitol, menthol, aloe vera, and clove oil for fresh breath.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"flex:1 1 280px;min-width:240px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #d7c9b8;border-radius:14px;padding:18px;\">\r\n          <h3 style=\"margin-top:0;\">Cool peppermint finish</h3>\r\n          <p style=\"color:#5a6b63;margin:0;\">Refreshing rinse with a clean,