-spacing:2px;color:#f1b400;font-size:1.05rem;\">★★★★★</div>\r\n            <p style=\"color:#5a6b63;margin:8px 0;\">\"Same fresh feeling as liquid mouthwash but no plastic waste. The tablets dissolve quickly and the cool peppermint finish is perfect. Will definitely repurchase.\"</p>\r\n            <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;\"><strong>— Omar Hassan</strong></p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div style=\"margin-top:16px;display:flex;justify-content:center;\">\r\n          <a href=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/products/zero-waste-mouthwash-tablets\"\r\n            rel=\"noopener\"\r\n            style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:999px;\r\n                   background:linear-gradient(180deg,#A1AB97,#1e6e4b);color:#fff;font-weight:800;border:0;\r\n                   box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(22,35,28,.10);text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;\">\r\n            Shop Mouthwash Tablets\r\n          </a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n$0",
